2
00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:17.120
Oh, crap!

3
00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:21.170
Who's there?

4
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.760
Th-They killed him!

5
00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.340
They actually offed Cobra!

6
00:00:31.340 --> 00:00:35.680
I may not have liked the guy,
but I haven't sunk so low I'd celebrate!

7
00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:38.850
I saw something I shouldn't have!

8
00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:51.490
I just had a brush with the dark side
of the World Government!

9
00:00:51.490 --> 00:00:53.280
I never asked for this!

10
00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:54.910
What was that thing?!

11
00:00:54.910 --> 00:00:57.160
My life is completely over!

12
00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:03.460
The Round Table
Conference Room

13
00:01:04.130 --> 00:01:08.130
King Cobra and King Wapol
have yet to arrive...

14
00:01:08.510 --> 00:01:10.590
We just received a message.

15
00:01:10.590 --> 00:01:13.300
They both requested
that you carry on without them.

16
00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:17.060
I guess King Cobra used up all his energy
on that impassioned speech!

17
00:01:19.270 --> 00:01:22.730
He must be satisfied with how
the matter of the Warlords was settled.

18
00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:24.400
Now then!

19
00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.860
Let's finish up the rest of our agenda.

20
00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:30.190
First, the independence of
the North Blue's Four-Nation Alliance...

21
00:01:31.070 --> 00:01:32.570
♪ Akamambo! ♪

22
00:01:32.570 --> 00:01:34.160
♪ Shake, shake! ♪

23
00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:35.740
Shirahoshi.

24
00:01:35.740 --> 00:01:37.870
The council will soon adjourn.

25
00:01:37.870 --> 00:01:40.330
Let's wait at the Red Port without these fools.

26
00:01:40.330 --> 00:01:41.460
Of course.

27
00:01:44.170 --> 00:01:44.960
What's wrong?

28
00:01:45.460 --> 00:01:49.340
I wanted to bid farewell to Princess Vivi.

29
00:01:49.960 --> 00:01:52.430
Wherever could she have gone?

30
00:01:52.470 --> 00:01:57.600
Guest Room
Pangaea Castle

31
00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:00.100
Why are you doing this?!

32
00:02:00.100 --> 00:02:01.560
Untie these ropes!

33
00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:03.020
Who ordered this?

34
00:02:03.020 --> 00:02:06.400
I'll tell the whole world what happened here!

35
00:02:08.110 --> 00:02:10.780
Whoa there, nobody likes a rat.

36
00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:13.860
What kind of idiot would
set you free after hearing that?

37
00:02:13.860 --> 00:02:15.570
You are one feisty lady!

38
00:02:15.570 --> 00:02:17.330
Jabra
Cipher Pol Aigis 0

39
00:02:18.870 --> 00:02:20.290
I hate to say it...

40
00:02:20.290 --> 00:02:23.290
but no one's coming to save you, Princess.

41
00:02:23.290 --> 00:02:27.540
You'll probably just be reported as "missing"
and wind up as someone's pet.

42
00:02:27.540 --> 00:02:28.750
Kalifa
Cipher Pol Aigis 0

43
00:02:28.750 --> 00:02:30.210
Is Shirahoshi okay?

44
00:02:30.210 --> 00:02:33.550
Seriously? Shouldn't you be worrying
about yourself right now?

45
00:02:37.010 --> 00:02:41.720
It sounds like there was another incident
earlier, but long story short, she's fine.

46
00:02:42.140 --> 00:02:43.430
Thank goodness...

47
00:02:43.430 --> 00:02:48.270
The guys who beat up the Celestial Dragon
trying to kidnap the mermaid...

48
00:02:49.270 --> 00:02:52.490
– We're Straw Hat Luffy's subordinates!
– We're Straw Hat Luffy's subordinates!

49
00:02:54.950 --> 00:02:59.660
...proudly declared themselves the winners
and sent the plaza into a frenzy.

50
00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:04.460
On top of that, in the Land of the Gods...

51
00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:09.210
Fujitora helped the Revolutionaries
free the slaves,

52
00:03:09.210 --> 00:03:11.960
which pissed off Ryokugyu,
and they got in a big fight...

53
00:03:12.460 --> 00:03:14.170
Sheesh...

54
00:03:14.170 --> 00:03:16.880
This year's Reverie has been one big mess.

55
00:03:18.090 --> 00:03:21.470
I have to do something... Be someone's pet?

56
00:03:22.010 --> 00:03:23.310
What a sick joke!

57
00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.400
Someone's...!

58
00:03:36.150 --> 00:03:38.110
Help me!

59
00:03:38.110 --> 00:03:40.780
I didn't see nothin'!

60
00:03:40.780 --> 00:03:41.780
Wapol?!

61
00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:43.620
Outta my way!

62
00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:44.450
That's it!

63
00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:50.380
Clear the way!

64
00:03:51.210 --> 00:03:52.550
I ain't...

65
00:03:53.300 --> 00:03:55.510
getting caught!

66
00:04:00.300 --> 00:04:02.720
What was that about?

67
00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:04.680
That was King Wapol, right?

68
00:04:06.930 --> 00:04:08.140
Hey, wait!

69
00:04:08.140 --> 00:04:09.600
Vivi's gone!

70
00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:11.360
What?!

71
00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:17.700
Hey!

72
00:04:18.910 --> 00:04:20.870
Salutations, Queen Kinderella.

73
00:04:20.870 --> 00:04:22.490
Have you seen my husband?

74
00:04:22.490 --> 00:04:24.990
No, I'm afraid I haven't.

75
00:04:31.500 --> 00:04:33.340
Oh, my!

76
00:04:31.790 --> 00:04:33.340
King Wapol!

77
00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:35.800
I've been looking for you, darling!

78
00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.800
Where have you been?!

79
00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:45.430
Who is that young woman?!

80
00:04:46.020 --> 00:04:48.180
Hey, Wapol! How far are you gonna go?!

81
00:04:48.180 --> 00:04:49.440
As far as I freakin' can!

82
00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:52.150
To the ends of the world
where no one will catch me!

83
00:04:52.650 --> 00:04:54.320
