Kamabakka Queendom
Peachy Island
Grand Line

233
00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:29.750
As soon as we arrived
at the Kingdom of Lulusia,

234
00:13:29.750 --> 00:13:32.250
King Seki and Princess Comane
were taken prisoner

235
00:13:32.620 --> 00:13:36.170
